{"id": 2625, "genre": 1001, "title": "什么时刻让你突然觉得同龄人心态上已经老了？", "description": "明明是被叫阿姨还会生气的年龄，怎么就突然做起微商了？（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA Images）", "record_count": 4414, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181112223505HJ7SzZoWnG8vucU4.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-11-21T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 312064, "content": "再也不问你现在喜欢什么。\n问你现在一个月挣多少钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 630, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 867167}, {"id": 312320, "content": "年轻人吃早餐哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1260683}, {"id": 312321, "content": "觉得需要承担家庭的责任的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1510433}, {"id": 312577, "content": "没有心情追星", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1511546}, {"id": 312066, "content": "开始不再追梦想，开始偏向平淡安稳", "image": null, "praise_count": 416, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1471298}, {"id": 312322, "content": "看新闻联播", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1205528}, {"id": 312578, "content": "有些人话题居然会聊到房价", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178872}, {"id": 312067, "content": "还在用Win7", "image": null, "praise_count": 85, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 982277}, {"id": 312323, "content": "开始随遇而安，放弃反抗生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1468904}, {"id": 313091, "content": "不再在意手机QQ连续在线天数了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1514494}, {"id": 313347, "content": "觉得看书是一件无聊的事。觉得你还是要谈恋爱结婚了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1516247}, {"id": 312325, "content": "开始变安静了，想东西变多了，你感觉到周围人对你看法不一样了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1510448}, {"id": 314117, "content": "开始关注脱发", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1519817}, {"id": 312070, "content": "开始注意关注食疗养生。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 316, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1120729}, {"id": 312326, "content": "开始有点佛系", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1506561}, {"id": 312327, "content": "发现要做的事有很多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1510448}, {"id": 313095, "content": "忽然想下班回家有个人在家等你", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513279}, {"id": 312328, "content": "从最开始的完全信任义无反顾的把自己的软肋喜爱告诉知道我发现你在利用我的软肋在对付我时起，，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1510454}, {"id": 313352, "content": "不再谈论梦想", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1516278}, {"id": 333065, "content": "……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1605759}, {"id": 313097, "content": "察觉到同龄人的幼稚", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1514606}, {"id": 315401, "content": "不管学啥，都开始想考公了。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455598}, {"id": 312074, "content": "金大侠走了，漫威之父斯坦李也离我们而去，李咏的声音再也听不到！80后的记忆越来越少了！真的老了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340202}, {"id": 312330, "content": "只是维持现有的稳定已花光我所有的力气", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1510461}, {"id": 316170, "content": "本是出去蹦迪的年龄，我想呆在家里泡脚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1234107}, {"id": 312075, "content": "把真正有爱好有坚持的人也说成装逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 452, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 801157}, {"id": 312331, "content": "发现过去的引以为豪不过是琐碎。悲伤才是人生的主调，但是人们很聪明把悲伤藏匿在身后然后继续工作为生活努力", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1507517}, {"id": 312332, "content": "突然想塞点钱给母亲", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497394}, {"id": 312588, "content": "看着好心酸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1447070}, {"id": 312077, "content": "平平淡淡才是真", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1160463}, {"id": 312333, "content": "总会想起爸爸妈妈当初为自己做的事情.", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508244}, {"id": 312589, "content": "看到优质小鲜肉或者年下男 世故老成的劝谏你 不要想了不可能的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333501}, {"id": 313101, "content": "开始觉得世界并不是小时候所想的那样，不是黑白分明，而是灰色的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1514629}, {"id": 312078, "content": "开始多关注父母，多陪伴他们", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1465280}, {"id": 312334, "content": "对好多事情都不再感兴趣，或者没那么大的兴趣，就像一个人静静的呆着", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039898}, {"id": 312335, "content": "以前在一起总是感叹，时间过的好慢啊，怎么还没到哪哪一天啊，现在碰面总是感叹，时间过得真快，又要到哪哪一天了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 134093}, {"id": 314895, "content": "讨论婚龄以及最佳生娃性价比", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1524108}, {"id": 312080, "content": "脱发和发胖，同时的！然后束手无策，懒得或无法改变···", "image": "img/option/option/20181121111606MFqIna5bOGAXZShr.jpeg", "praise_count": 221, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1349071}, {"id": 313616, "content": "开始收集塑料袋了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1327849}, {"id": 314896, "content": "原来信心满满留下，如今准备回家谋生", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1524108}, {"id": 312081, "content": "从社会大学毕业的那一刻", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697948}, {"id": 313105, "content": "睡得越来越早，不再太晚睡觉，再也不执着于另一个人，朋友之间要互相尊重的才可惜拥有，其他的都不重要", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1514758}, {"id": 312082, "content": "开始注重养生", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1494902}, {"id": 312594, "content": "总是在思考，总是在担忧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1435671}, {"id": 312595, "content": "注意饮食 不熬夜 早起 \n我老了👿", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1511536}, {"id": 313619, "content": "开始上班了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1517236}, {"id": 312084, "content": "不再任性地乞求别人的关注，开始学会倾听和陪伴了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 74, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1505362}, {"id": 314132, "content": "堂而皇之的表达工作中对年轻人的不满", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271976}, {"id": 312085, "content": "我说“”你好，我们上床吧” 她回答“这算是骚扰吧”", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1360023}, {"id": 312341, "content": "开始将就着找个男朋友将就着谈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434274}]}